OL,3,CAngela Rayner confirms Awaab's Law is
OL,4,Cto be extended to protect private
OL,5,Crenters
OL,7,FA law named after a toddler from
OL,8,FRochdale which aims to protect social
OL,9,Ftenants from mouldy homes is set to be
OL,10,Fextended to privately rented housing.
OL,12,FTwo-year-old Awaab died In a mould-
OL,13,Finfested flat in Rochdale in December
OL,14,F2020 owned by housing association
OL,15,FRochdale Boroughwide Housing.
OL,17,FAwaab's Law was brought in by the
OL,18,FConservative government last year as
OL,19,Fpart of the landmark Social Housing
OL,20,FRegulation Bill.
