OL,3,CAngela Rayner confirms Awaab's Law is
OL,4,Cto be extended to protect private
OL,5,Crenters
OL,7,FIt requires landlords to fix hazards
OL,8,Fthat pose a danger to tenants' health
OL,9,Fwith a strict, legal time limit, but
OL,10,Fthe law only applies to properties in
OL,11,Fthe social housing sector.
OL,13,FToday the deputy Labour Leader Angela
OL,14,FRayner confirmed at the Labour party
OL,15,Fconference in Liverpool that Awaab's
OL,16,FLaw would be in place this autumn.
