OL,3,CAngela Rayner confirms Awaab's Law is
OL,4,Cto be extended to protect private
OL,5,Crenters
OL,7,FAngela Rayner said: "Many Housing
OL,8,FAssociations, councils and landlords
OL,9,Fdo good by their tenants and I know
OL,10,Fhow hard they've had it after 14 years
OL,11,Funder the Tories. Which is why I will
OL,12,Fwork in partnership with the sector to
OL,13,Fdeliver the change. I will clamp down
OL,14,Fon damp and mouldy homes by bringing
OL,15,Fin Awaab's Law in the social rented
OL,16,Fsector this autumn and we'll extend it
OL,17,Fto the private rented sector too."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
