OL,3,CAngela Rayner confirms Awaab's Law is
OL,4,Cto be extended to protect private
OL,5,Crenters
OL,7,FChristian Weaver, the barrister who
OL,8,Frepresented the family of Awaab Ishak,
OL,9,Fthe two-year-old boy whose tragic
OL,10,Fdeath was linked to prolonged exposure
OL,11,Fto mould in his home, said he welcomed
OL,12,Fnews of the extension.
OL,14,FHe said he had been advocating for
OL,15,Fsome time for Awaab's Law to extend
OL,16,Fbeyond social housing to the private
OL,17,Frented sector.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
