OL,3,CAngela Rayner confirms Awaab's Law is
OL,4,Cto be extended to protect private
OL,5,Crenters
OL,7,FMr Weaver said: "This law must be
OL,8,Fpaired with a robust education
OL,9,Fcampaign to ensure tenants understand
OL,10,Ftheir rights. It is essential that
OL,11,Fsystems are in place to provide legal
OL,12,Faid and support for tenants wishing to
OL,13,Ftake action in court if a breach of
OL,14,FAwaab's Law occurs, particularly for
OL,15,Fthose who might not otherwise have the
OL,16,Fmeans to do so."
